    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo describes Version 1.5 of the client/server interaction of RWhois.  RWhois provides a distributed system for the discovery, retrieval, and maintenance of directory information.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
